summary: AN ORDINANCE accepting easements over portions of Blocks 376 and 386 of the Seattle Tide Lands, 6th Avenue South as vacated by Ordinance 28873, Government Lot 1 in Section 18, Township 24 North, Range 4 East, W.M. and portion of Duwamish East Waterway as vacated November 10, 1969 for perpetual street easements. (West Seattle Bridge Replacement Project; RW 7855).
